{"tid":82682,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"免去職務 免去原本個意思唔係 罷免 咩","createTime":"2017-01-16T06:46:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-16T10:42:31.000Z","uid":29804,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5c47f6f942b10df249f65b18aae948917f78a6a0","tid":82682,"uid":29804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T06:46:46.000Z","msg":"接納請辭<br />\n唔係更好咩<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n免去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c29b2340f0f6cb9803b118d19c4774fd62fcaa3","tid":82682,"uid":17691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T06:48:55.000Z","msg":"反映權在我手<br />\n係我罷免你 唔係你辭職<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c8daaf09a2e3a70458209fe6ab2acf1bfbf8706","tid":82682,"uid":9230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T06:53:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>接納請辭<br />\n唔係更好咩<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n免去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n共產黨文法免去XX職務係中性詞彙，同「離任」一樣啫，就算升職都會「免去」舊職務先嘅。<br />\n<br />\n就算台灣一樣有呢啲獨特嘅政治用語"},{"pid":"40a498fde532b6db6b5819be932de34fadc82bd9","tid":82682,"uid":29804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T06:53:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>接納請辭<br />\n唔係更好咩<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n免去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n共產黨文法免去XX職務係中性詞彙，同「離任」一樣啫，就算升職都會「免去」舊職務先嘅。<br />\n<br />\n就算台灣一樣有呢啲獨特嘅政治用語</blockquote><br />\n台灣用咩"},{"pid":"8e16bab02afab2b6f04fb3105b01eff6f2329cb8","tid":82682,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T06:53:42.000Z","msg":"所以我一向好撚憎大陸狗用字"},{"pid":"4459ef4dae9508e1f1f3f78f18d2045a5ff75a68","tid":82682,"uid":50329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T06:54:34.000Z","msg":"1. 唔好以為見到漢字你就一定會明<br />\n2. 佢係外國語文<br />\n3. 道理等同你見到「大丈夫」「精一杯」「勉強」，你唔可以用本國語文知識去理解外國語文"},{"pid":"fbefdb5918858913f710a490656f951d2a0a4057","tid":82682,"uid":38255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T06:57:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>1. 唔好以為見到漢字你就一定會明<br />\n2. 佢係外國語文<br />\n3. 道理等同你見到「大丈夫」「精一杯」「勉強」，你唔可以用本國語文知識去理解外國語文</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n支語同漢語係兩種語言<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6722fa5d4d8722b0785fcf04e04b2f098119e529","tid":82682,"uid":807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T07:01:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>接納請辭<br />\n唔係更好咩<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n免去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n共產黨文法免去XX職務係中性詞彙，同「離任」一樣啫，就算升職都會「免去」舊職務先嘅。<br />\n<br />\n就算台灣一樣有呢啲獨特嘅政治用語</blockquote><br />\n台灣用咩</blockquote><br />\n我剩係知台灣一啲用語係跟日本<br />\n例如 現行犯 不起訴處分"},{"pid":"f527bc9ad9b8c60f1ce2d69df86bd9bb7462ca29","tid":82682,"uid":9230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T07:09:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>接納請辭<br />\n唔係更好咩<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n免去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n共產黨文法免去XX職務係中性詞彙，同「離任」一樣啫，就算升職都會「免去」舊職務先嘅。<br />\n<br />\n就算台灣一樣有呢啲獨特嘅政治用語</blockquote><br />\n台灣用咩</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n都係會用免職<br />\n<br />\n所謂任免，有「任」用就有「免」職<br />\n<br />\n譯做英文即係Appointment 同 discharge <br />\n其實係中性詞。<br />\n<br />\n如果係被罷免，個負面係負喺個「罷」字唔係個「免」字度<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmdbcC4aEFKgcDTZAUw5zffwxfwXaNQ5ugJ5jXDixhu15d?filename=RqiVCrz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRqiVCrz.jpg&h=470185bf&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6b921da6079a5bf891244631826b40bdc5ba1c54","tid":82682,"uid":50329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T07:20:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>接納請辭<br />\n唔係更好咩<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n免去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n共產黨文法免去XX職務係中性詞彙，同「離任」一樣啫，就算升職都會「免去」舊職務先嘅。<br />\n<br />\n就算台灣一樣有呢啲獨特嘅政治用語</blockquote><br />\n台灣用咩</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n都係會用免職<br />\n<br />\n所謂任免，有「任」用就有「免」職<br />\n<br />\n譯做英文即係Appointment 同 discharge <br />\n其實係中性詞。<br />\n<br />\n如果係被罷免，個負面係負喺個「罷」字唔係個「免」字度<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmdbcC4aEFKgcDTZAUw5zffwxfwXaNQ5ugJ5jXDixhu15d?filename=RqiVCrz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRqiVCrz.jpg&h=470185bf&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢度係香港<br />\n你攞外國文獻嚟做乜柒 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"893b853fee5ff75ae9d64275de81da06db5cce2b","tid":82682,"uid":38781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T09:08:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n台灣用咩</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n都係會用免職<br />\n<br />\n所謂任免，有「任」用就有「免」職<br />\n<br />\n譯做英文即係Appointment 同 discharge <br />\n其實係中性詞。<br />\n<br />\n如果係被罷免，個負面係負喺個「罷」字唔係個「免」字度<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmdbcC4aEFKgcDTZAUw5zffwxfwXaNQ5ugJ5jXDixhu15d?filename=RqiVCrz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRqiVCrz.jpg&h=470185bf&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢度係香港<br />\n你攞外國文獻嚟做乜柒 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n台灣都叫外國文獻，同你講中文就話引錯外國文獻，究竟係你識得少字定還是政府柒頭皮用左大陸蝗話，咁撚有求真精神不如去問下品客點睇。"},{"pid":"3a3ece02b4b4d3572e23c9abceda1134ee0e4774","tid":82682,"uid":807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T09:10:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n都係會用免職<br />\n<br />\n所謂任免，有「任」用就有「免」職<br />\n<br />\n譯做英文即係Appointment 同 discharge <br />\n其實係中性詞。<br />\n<br />\n如果係被罷免，個負面係負喺個「罷」字唔係個「免」字度<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmdbcC4aEFKgcDTZAUw5zffwxfwXaNQ5ugJ5jXDixhu15d?filename=RqiVCrz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRqiVCrz.jpg&h=470185bf&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢度係香港<br />\n你攞外國文獻嚟做乜柒 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n台灣都叫外國文獻，同你講中文就話引錯外國文獻，究竟係你識得少字定還是政府柒頭皮用左大陸蝗話，咁撚有求真精神不如去問下品客點睇。</blockquote><br />\n台灣點解唔係外國文獻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b2d16cdc0beea92a0ece0755870ea1bd3e7a77e","tid":82682,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T09:23:32.000Z","msg":"免治牛肉飯"},{"pid":"38eae02cd785c944caf6a91b84e78a8017decbb8","tid":82682,"uid":47210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T09:25:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>1. 唔好以為見到漢字你就一定會明<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">2. 佢係外國語文</span><br />\n3. 道理等同你見到「大丈夫」「精一杯」「勉強」，你唔可以用本國語文知識去理解外國語文</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be82e2d3075c5e4464f513cdb07b309e0450b756","tid":82682,"uid":70527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T09:25:56.000Z","msg":"免去 係中性<br />\n罷免 係負面<br />\n咁解釋得唔得"},{"pid":"3d9a90bc47112f9867208bba0751957813a5430c","tid":82682,"uid":9230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T10:42:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>免去 係中性<br />\n罷免 係負面<br />\n咁解釋得唔得</blockquote><br />\n無錯，個免字本身無負面含意"}]}